Version 1.2 - January 5, 2009
    * Syntax change: A dash before each section, subsection and frame 
      is no longer required
    * Support for Metadata directly in the YAML document
    * Auto-escape LaTeX special characters
    * Possibility to pass options to the image command
    * Use optparse for parsing command-line options
    * Search for code files relative from the .yml file's path
    * Made Pygments optional. If Pygments cannot be found, the source 
      code will be included but not highlighted
    
Version 1.1 - October 16, 2008
    * Dropped idiopidae and zapps dependency as the code is now 
      highlighted directly through Pygments
    * Create setup.py file and make package easy_install-able

Version 1.0 - June 23, 2008
    * Initial release based off of Zed Shaw's script.